---
title: Double Smokey Chicken & Slaw Burger with Aioli & Fries
description: Those smokey flavours are magical, they have the unbeatable power to make your mouth water. The chicken is stacked up in a burger and smeared with smokey aioli to cast a spell on your tastebuds. The only way to break the spell is, of course, to dig in and devour the fries and chicken burger!
